## Reason Numeric value	Constant	Meaning
  0	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_UNDEFINED	Normal boot (not from sleep)
  1	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_ALL	Not commonly used
  2	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_EXT0	Wake from external GPIO (EXT0)
  3	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_EXT1	Wake from multiple GPIOs (EXT1)
  4	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_TIMER	Wake from timer
  5	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_TOUCHPAD	Wake from touch sensor
  6	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_ULP	Wake from ULP coprocessor
  7	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_GPIO	GPIO wake (legacy/variant)
  8	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_UART	UART wake
  9	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_WIFI	Wake from WiFi (rare use)
  10	ESP_SLEEP_WAKEUP_COCPU	Co-processor wake
